data.description:
MUST SEE!

Close to downtown, close to I-75. All newer windows, roof and vinyl siding. Breaker boxes. Brand new kitchen cabinets, counters and flooring. New carpet and pad throughout. Fresh coat of paint everywhere in a neutral palette. 2 full baths, one upstairs, one downstairs. 4 bedrooms, 2 up/2 down. Large living room. Eat-in kitchen. Large laundry/utility room. Basement.
data.whatILove: This home has been completely re-done. It has 2 full baths. 4 bedrooms, large living room, large kitchen with brand new cabinets and counters. New flooring throughout (carpet, linoleum. All electrical is breaker. All plumbing is new. Ready to move in!  Close to downtown. Minutes from I-75. All new windows. Could be turned into a duplex VERY easily.
